{"tid":1595474,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭白兔 其實好慘......!","createTime":"2019-09-26T05:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T15:34:07.000Z","uid":197098,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"132028a0d8e748cb980a2dea9d9b0f75c1c634e0","tid":1595474,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭白兔(New Zealand White)多數被用來做實驗，壽命只有幾日至幾個月 (例如: Bodyshop 有做過) 有些人不喜歡牠因為有粉紅色眼睛，但其實這個品種好善良，又好幽默。我見過兔協有2-3隻，隨時可領養。<br />\n<br />\n領養了New Zealand White，瘋狂跳兔子舞:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=0b57736c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a>"},{"pid":"0fa9b74b5b99a3f1871ef11e2a30db4e0260891f","tid":1595474,"uid":277920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778a9f4db53cb9fd538880541a89a5b0f418032e","tid":1595474,"uid":254923,"like":5,"dislike":18,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"0fa9b74b5b99a3f1871ef11e2a30db4e0260891f","tid":1595474,"uid":277920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"好好食添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e053359086a15f1af926346308c56f071efc9c","tid":1595474,"uid":180421,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"幽默啫係點？佢識講笑話？"},{"pid":"5aded42caa28dd44026b92db8a1632c838aeff12","tid":1595474,"uid":250147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06e053359086a15f1af926346308c56f071efc9c","tid":1595474,"uid":180421,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"幽默啫係點？佢識講笑話？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a570254e8deac005edb24c12686757097e91ed0","tid":1595474,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"（有圖）各師兄弟 歸位未？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595382</a>"},{"pid":"834a37e0c31b1e04d289b0e6c5cdda40d150ea69","tid":1595474,"uid":252609,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"樓主重複又重複咁開d兔仔post做乜9，開咗成年都冇人討論，不如你改一改d內容，唔好齋copy好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"233da9ac24c2d65b2de530d6713db4826f30e87d","tid":1595474,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">寵物兔是應該要被絕育</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"99406d3f0d7639fabcfb3d6965f391cfc922594e","tid":1595474,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"834a37e0c31b1e04d289b0e6c5cdda40d150ea69","tid":1595474,"uid":252609,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"樓主重複又重複咁開d兔仔post做乜9，開咗成年都冇人討論，不如你改一改d內容，唔好齋copy好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T19:47:28.000Z","msg":"樓主AI黎<br />\n佢有啲po會打啲唔隔行勁大段痴埋一齊既英文 好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469d073ed62808598ea3894dcf58e8420d2a1b7f","tid":1595474,"uid":217411,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"778a9f4db53cb9fd538880541a89a5b0f418032e","tid":1595474,"uid":254923,"like":5,"dislike":18,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"0fa9b74b5b99a3f1871ef11e2a30db4e0260891f","tid":1595474,"uid":277920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"好好食添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T19:50:48.000Z","msg":"你呢種人渣<br />\n下世做返動物畀人食返就岩喇"},{"pid":"fd8cdcd59f4ff0885ab890e949f767ccde0f34e8","tid":1595474,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有些人會問: 為什麼我在東, 牠會面向著西?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實兔子<strong><ins>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</ins></strong>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<strong><ins>你在牠後面也會看到你</ins></strong>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">親人的動物：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=9204a68a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=cd88530d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兔子的行為解釋網站：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=475f4bae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=4af1cfda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=92a27163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"d3c3b477edae6cfaa99dcde4ac54cca401824076","tid":1595474,"uid":198402,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:53:48.000Z","msg":"起完底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38a3cd7a3cf753c3bf3d096f24a822895e3afb2","tid":1595474,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b705275b0a3671fe190101cbf584a5834ae83bc8","tid":1595474,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb32367814080244f5bca8046f9bcfb9a0dac8b","tid":1595474,"